description:
Booby Trap Ridge!

This is the story of a soldier whose job was to sweep the roads in advance of the infantry! It would have been an easy job if his "broom" hadn't been a mine detector -- and the "dust" he picked up wasn't saturated with high explosives!

Veteran Rookie!

He would have given anything not to have drawn this assignment! He thought the army had made a mistake! He found out otherwise!

Life Of A Dog Tag!

Two identical small pieces of metal worn by every soldier on which is stamped his identity and blood type are the silent characters of -- Life of a Dog Tag!

Blow Torch Pilots (Text only story)

Frogman's Secret!

You're Harry Brown, underwater demolition team leader, USN, one of Father Neptune's foster sons! Your name, rank, and serial number are all you're required to give as a prisoner! But right now, the Nazi Captain holding that Luger to your head wants to know more -- much more!
name: Booby Trap Ridge!; Veteran Rookie!; Life Of A Dog Tag!; Blow Torch Pilots; Frogman's Secret!

description:
Plot Summary

This issue of My Greatest Adventure contains the following five stories:

  • I Was King of Dagger Island!
  • I Hunted a Flying Saucer!
  • Trapped By a Twister!
  • My Cargo Was Death!
  • Primitive Hunter!

I Was King of Dagger Island

When Eddie Doyle, a First Class Seaman, and Lt. Howell are headed towards Palu Island their boat is attacked with a barrage of torpedoes. As the only survivors of the wreck they feel as if their luck can't get any better; however, this all changes when they wash up on shore of a mysterious island and meet the natives.

I Hunted a Flying Saucer!

Pilot John Marston is flying high when a strange object passes by at high speeds. When Marston's curiosity gets the best of him he discovers the object is a flying saucer! Will anyone believe Marston's story or is he headed straight for the insanity ward?

Trapped By a Twister!

Jim and his wife are spending a nice day out on their farm when a tornado strikes terror into their hearts! Can the duo escape this elemental assault?

My Cargo Was Death!

Barney and Ed knew they didn't want to be responsible for delivering an explosive nitro shipment to Camp #7; however, Barney's emotions get the better of him as he's guilt tripped into the job. Barney begins to regret the trip as he faces bandits, bullets and a barrage of bombs!

Primitive Hunter!

Man versus beast in the one-page epic. How shall man fare when he's reduced to his most basic instincts against the might of a super gorilla?!
name: My Cargo Was Death
